hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 直接驱动能量平衡：吸收的能量为
$$E_{abs,DD}=E_{L,DD}\,\eta_{abs}$$  
内爆动能为
$$K_{imp}=\eta_H(x_{DD})\,E_{abs,DD} = \eta_H(x_{DD})\,E_{L,DD}\,\eta_{abs}\,. $$  
因此
$$E_{L,DD}=\frac{K_{imp}}{\eta_{abs}\,\eta_H(x_{DD})}\,. $$

2. 间接驱动能量平衡：靶丸吸收的能量为
$$E_{abs,ID}=E_{L,ID}\,\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}$$  
且
$$K_{imp}=\eta_H(x_{ID})\,E_{abs,ID} = \eta_H(x_{ID})\,E_{L,ID}\,\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}\,. $$  
因此
$$E_{L,ID}=\frac{K_{imp}}{\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}\,\eta_H(x_{ID})}\,. $$

3. 所需激光能量之比：
$$\mathcal R=\frac{E_{L,ID}}{E_{L,DD}}
=\frac{\displaystyle\frac{K_{imp}}{\eta_{L-X}f_{geom}\,\eta_H(x_{ID})}}
{\displaystyle\frac{K_{imp}}{\eta_{abs}\,\eta_H(x_{DD})}}
=\frac{\eta_{abs}\,\eta_H(x_{DD})}{\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}\,\eta_H(x_{ID})}\,. $$

4. 代入 $\displaystyle\eta_H(x)=\frac{x}{2(1-x)}\bigl(\ln\frac1x\bigr)^2$ 消去因子 $2$，得到
$$
\mathcal R
=\frac{\eta_{abs}}{\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}}
\frac{x_{DD}/(1-x_{DD})}{x_{ID}/(1-x_{ID})}
\left(\frac{\ln\frac1{x_{DD}}}{\ln\frac1{x_{ID}}}\right)^{2}
=\frac{\eta_{abs}}{\eta_{L-X}\,f_{geom}}
\frac{x_{DD}(1-x_{ID})}{x_{ID}(1-x_{DD})}
\left(\frac{\ln\frac1{x_{DD}}}{\ln\frac1{x_{ID}}}\right)^{2}\,. $$
